This is an example application for the XCommon CMake build system.

To build:
  cmake -G "Unix Makefiles" -B build
  xmake -C build

To make factory image:
  cd bin
  xflash xmos-ddc.xe -o factory.bin

To make dfu image:
  cd bin
  xflash --factory-version 15.3 --upgrade 1 xmos-ddc.xe -o upgrade1.bin

To flash dfu image:
  dfu-util -d 20b1:0018,20b1:d018 -D upgrade1.bin -R
